{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2019/march","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"custom-fields-beta\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#custom-fields-beta\" aria-label=\"custom fields beta permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Custom Fields (beta)</h3>\n<p>We introduce <a href=\"/programs/custom-fields.html\">custom fields</a> to enable programs to add custom information to their reports to help them better manage and analyze their internal data by the categories that they define to be important. This feature is only available for Enterprise programs.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.800000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"custom fields page\"\n        title=\"custom fields page\"\n        src=\"/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/0b533/mar_2019_custom_fields.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/fac75/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 125w,\n/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/63868/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 250w,\n/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/0b533/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 500w,\n/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/1d69c/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 750w,\n/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/00d43/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 1000w,\n/static/51fbd39f3ab0120007c2b4b43d2e322d/f1c64/mar_2019_custom_fields.png 1390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"custom-fields-on-the-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#custom-fields-on-the-api\" aria-label=\"custom fields on the api permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Custom Fields on the API</h3>\n<p>We've also added custom fields to the API to enable programs to search and filter reports by <a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#reports-manage-custom-field-values\">custom field values</a>.     </p>\n<h3 id=\"program-notifications-beta\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#program-notifications-beta\" aria-label=\"program notifications beta permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Program Notifications (beta)</h3>\n<p>Select hackers now receive program notifications to all program updates via the product and email for changes to the:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Policy</li>\n<li>Bounty table</li>\n<li>Scope</li>\n<li>Hacker messages</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 123.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"program notifications\"\n        title=\"program notifications\"\n        src=\"/static/fa84767ad580ad6b5a61b842ed57d317/0b533/mar_2019_program_notifications_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa84767ad580ad6b5a61b842ed57d317/fac75/mar_2019_program_notifications_1.png 125w,\n/static/fa84767ad580ad6b5a61b842ed57d317/63868/mar_2019_program_notifications_1.png 250w,\n/static/fa84767ad580ad6b5a61b842ed57d317/0b533/mar_2019_program_notifications_1.png 500w,\n/static/fa84767ad580ad6b5a61b842ed57d317/f941f/mar_2019_program_notifications_1.png 736w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>We've also implemented a new <strong>Subscribe</strong> button on the policy page to enable hackers to easily subscribe to program notifications. <em>Note: The button is currently viewable for select hackers.</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.399999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAcklEQVQI142Oyw7CMBAD8/+fyIkLFA5NWnY3Jc8hrVSJYy2NbPlg2THUe79MS5kShBa/tFyopVLrYGQzw3nvCSGw+z97d/anqyo20OWD3CfiNJO9kt4reRZsFZyIcJVjcLywaOgW2RahPALp9iI/wzH4A9R05+uYkdF0AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"subscribe button\"\n        title=\"subscribe button\"\n        src=\"/static/bffa167ea10455349f7c5f041e91e5cf/0b533/mar_2019_program_notifications-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bffa167ea10455349f7c5f041e91e5cf/fac75/mar_2019_program_notifications-2.png 125w,\n/static/bffa167ea10455349f7c5f041e91e5cf/63868/mar_2019_program_notifications-2.png 250w,\n/static/bffa167ea10455349f7c5f041e91e5cf/0b533/mar_2019_program_notifications-2.png 500w,\n/static/bffa167ea10455349f7c5f041e91e5cf/d67ca/mar_2019_program_notifications-2.png 714w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"deprecation-of-custom-recipients-for-messaging-hackers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deprecation-of-custom-recipients-for-messaging-hackers\" aria-label=\"deprecation of custom recipients for messaging hackers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Deprecation of Custom Recipients for Messaging Hackers</h3>\n<p>We've deprecated the <em>Custom</em> recipient field on the Message Hackers page as the feature wasn't found to be very valuable for programs.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2019/march","title":"March 2019"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}